us_X" title="Pope Pius X">Pius X</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_Benedict_XV" title="Pope Benedict XV">Benedict XV</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_Pius_XI" title="Pope Pius XI">Pius XI</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_Pius_XII" title="Pope Pius XII">Pius XII</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_John_XXIII" title="Pope John XXIII">John XXIII</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_Paul_VI" title="Pope Paul VI">Paul VI</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_John_Paul_I" title="Pope John Paul I">John Paul I</a> <br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_John_Paul_II" title="Pope John Paul II">John Paul II</a><br /><a href="/wiki/Pope_Benedict_XVI" title="Pope Benedict XVI">Benedict XVI</a><br /><a class="mw-selflink selflink">Francis</a>
